Ansible hosts file for connecting to multi os like ubuntu , linux , redhat

sudo nano /etc/ansible/hosts
[test]
ubuntu server private IP
[servers]
linux-server ansible_host=172.31.43.185 ansible_user=ec2-user
redhat-server ansible_host=172.31.40.142 ansible_user=ec2-user
# Next save this by ctrl+o , enter, ctrl+x


Ansible hosts for connecting same OS like only ubuntu or only linux

sudo nano /etc/ansible/hosts
[test]
NODE1 PRIVATE IP
[QA]
NODE2 PRIVATE IP
[PROD]
NODE3 PRIVATE IP
